# the [[Korean]] [[language]]

====Usage notes====
Of the many Korean names for the Korean language, this is the most formal in the Republic of Korea (South Korea). {{ko-l|한국말}} is more commonly used, but it denotes exclusively the spoken language (말 (mal) is speech). In North Korea, {{ko-l|조선말}} is more common.

